#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--param</option> key=value"
msgstr "<option>--param</option> nyckel=värde"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set parameters to pass to the stylesheet."
msgstr "Ställ in parametrar att skicka till stilmallen."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Användning"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"Det vanligaste sättet att köra <command>meinproc6</command> är helt enkelt "
"som <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-fil</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> där <replaceable>docbook-fil</replaceable> oftast är index."
"docbook. Kommandot skapar &HTML;-sidor från DocBook-filen. Observera att "
"sidorna bara går att titta på i &kde;-baserade webbläsare (som &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Om du behöver visa &HTML;-utmatningen i en annan webbläsare (om du till "
"exempel gör den direkt tillgänglig på nätet), använd <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet "
"<replaceable>stilmallsnamn</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-fil</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> där <replaceable>stilmallsnamn</replaceable> är den "
"fullständiga sökvägen till en av &XSL;-stilmallarna i  &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. För "
"att skapa utmatning lämplig för webben, kan du använda <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> eller <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. Se filen "
"<filename>README</filename> i den katalogen för mer detaljerad information."

